&lt;div class=&quot;reveal-modal&quot; id=&quot;exampleModal&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h2&gt;
		This is a modal.&lt;/h2&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;
		Reveal makes these very easy to summon and dismiss. The close button is simple an anchor with a unicode character icon and a class of &lt;code&gt;close-reveal-modal&lt;/code&gt;. Clicking anywhere outside the modal will also dismiss it.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;a class=&quot;close-reveal-modal&quot;&gt;Ã—&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
