			&lt;div class=&quot;eight columns&quot;&gt;
				&lt;a name=&quot;offsets&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
				&lt;h3&gt;
					Offsets&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div class=&quot;four columns tabs&quot;&gt;
				&lt;dl class=&quot;tabs pill small&quot;&gt;
					&lt;dd class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;
						&lt;a href=&quot;#offsetsEx&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/dd&gt;
					&lt;dd&gt;
						&lt;a href=&quot;#offsetsCode&quot;&gt;Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/dd&gt;
				&lt;/dl&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;
			Offsets allow you to create additional space between columns in a row. The offsets run from offset-by-one all the way up to offset-by-eleven. Like the rest of the grid, they&#039;re nestable.&lt;/p&gt;
